    <article>
        <p>Focus is the key to unlocking your full potential. It's the ability to concentrate on a single task or idea without being distracted by external stimuli. Whether you're working on a project, studying for an exam, or simply trying to relax, focus is essential for achieving your goals.</p>
        <h2>Why Focus Matters</h2>
        <p>Focus helps you stay on track and avoid procrastination. It allows you to prioritize tasks and make better decisions. When you're focused, you're more productive and less likely to make mistakes.</p>
        <blockquote>
            "Focus is the ability to concentrate on a single task or idea without being distracted by external stimuli."
        </blockquote>
        <p>So, how can you improve your focus? Here are some tips:</p>
